'''Ermin Mahmić''' ({{IPA|bs|ěrmin mâːxmitɕ|pron}}; born 14 March 2005) is a professional [[Association football|footballer]] who plays as an [[Midfielder#Attacking midfielder|attacking midfielder]] for [[Czech First League]] club [[FC Slovan Liberec|Slovan Liberec]]. Born in Austria, he plays for the [[Bosnia and Herzegovina national football team|Bosnia and Herzegovina national team]].

Mahmić started his professional career at [[SV Lafnitz]], before joining Slovan Liberec in 2025.

A former Austrian youth international, Mahmić made his senior international debut for Bosnia and Herzegovina in 2026.

==Club career==

===Early career===
Mahmić started playing football at his hometown club ESV Intersport Wels, which he joined in 2011. The following year, he switched to [[FC Pasching|FC Pasching's youth setup]]. In 2015, he moved to [[LASK|LASK's youth academy]]. Four years later, he joined [[SK Rapid Wien|Rapid Wien's youth setup]]. In July 2023, Mahmić signed with [[SV Lafnitz]]. He made his professional debut against [[SV Stripfing]] on 20 October at the age of 18. On 23 August 2024, he scored his first professional goal against the same opponent.<ref>{{cite news|url=https://radiosarajevo.ba/sport/nogomet/ko-je-novi-zmaj-ermin-mahmic-zbog-bih-je-dva-puta-izdao-austriju/635725|title=Ko je novi Zmaj Ermin Mahmić: Zbog BiH je dva puta "izdao" Austriju|website=radiosarajevo.ba|date=1 May 2026|access-date=1 May 2026|language=bs}}</ref>

In June 2025, he moved to Czech team [[FC Slovan Liberec|Slovan Liberec]].<ref>{{cite news|url=https://laola1.at/de/red/fussball/2--liga/news/oefb-talent-verlaesst-absteiger-lafnitz-in-richtung-tschechien|title=ÖFB-Talent verlässt Absteiger Lafnitz in Richtung Tschechien|website=laola1.at|date=5 June 2025|access-date=5 June 2025|language=de}}</ref>

==International career==
After representing [[Austria national football team|Austria]] at various youth levels, and also [[Bosnia and Herzegovina national football team|Bosnia and Herzegovina]] at the [[Bosnia and Herzegovina national under-19 football team|under-19]] level, Mahmić decided to play for Bosnia and Herzegovina at the senior level.<ref>{{cite news|url=https://n1info.ba/sport/nogomet/emir-spahic-pronasao-novo-pojacanje-za-reprezentaciju-bih-dobro-nam-dosao-sine-bosanski|title=Emir Spahić pronašao novo pojačanje za reprezentaciju BiH: Dobro nam došao sine bosanski!|website=n1info.ba|date=1 May 2026|access-date=1 May 2026|language=bs}}</ref>

In May 2026, his request to change sports citizenship from Austrian to Bosnian was approved by [[FIFA]].<ref>{{cite news|url=https://faktor.ba/sport/fudbal/fsbih-se-pohvalio-velikom-pobjedom-bit-ce-na-raspolaganju-selektoru-sergeju-barbarezu-za-predstojece-izazove/252844|title=FSBiH se pohvalio velikom pobjedom: Bit će na raspolaganju selektoru Sergeju Barbarezu za predstojeće izazove|website=faktor.com|date=1 May 2026|access-date=1 May 2026|language=bs}}</ref> He debuted in a [[Exhibition game#Association football|friendly]] game against [[North Macedonia national football team|North Macedonia]] on 29 May.<ref>{{cite news|url=https://oslobodjenje.ba/sport/fudbal/reprezentacija/foto-sergej-barbarez-podijelio-minutazu-reprezentativcima-remi-na-kosevu|title=Sergej Barbarez podijelio minutažu reprezentativcima, remi na Koševu|website=oslobodjenje.ba|date=29 May 2026|access-date=1 June 2026|language=bs}}</ref>

In June 2026, Mahmić was named in Bosnia and Herzegovina's squad for the [[2026 FIFA World Cup]].<ref>{{cite news|url=https://sportske.ba/clanak/barbarez-poslao-konacan-spisak-fifa-i-jedno-ime-otputovalo-u-ameriku-ali-nije-na-listi|title=Barbarez poslao konačan spisak FIFA-i: Jedno ime otputovalo u Ameriku, ali nije na listi|website=sportske.ba|date=3 June 2026|access-date=3 June 2026|language=bs}}</ref>

== Personal life ==
Mahmić's father was born in [[Mahmić Selo]] near [[Bosanska Krupa]], while his mother is from [[Bihać]].<ref>{{Cite web |last=T.Š |date=2026-05-11 |title=(VIDEO) Ko je Ermin Mahmić, novi fudbalski reprezentativac BiH? |url=https://www.oslobodjenje.ba/sport/fudbal/reprezentacija/video-ko-je-ermin-mahmic-novi-fudbalski-reprezentativac-bi-h/ |access-date=2026-06-06 |website=Oslobođenje |language=bs}}</ref>

